414
00:19:13,119 --> 00:19:14,888
[MINORI] WHY NOT?

415
00:19:14,988 --> 00:19:16,489
[TOYA] I DON'T KNOW.

416
00:19:16,590 --> 00:19:19,092
HE WAS SO COOL AND
NICE AND EVERYTHING.

417
00:19:19,192 --> 00:19:21,361
HE'S SUPER SMART.

418
00:19:21,461 --> 00:19:24,865
HE'S JUST AMAZING,
RIGHT? I JUST...

419
00:19:24,965 --> 00:19:27,367
[MINORI] YEAH.

420
00:19:27,467 --> 00:19:29,235
[MINORI, THINKING]
HE'S RIGHT.

421
00:19:29,335 --> 00:19:33,373
BUT WE HAVE NO RIGHT
TO ASK HIM TO GET
US OUT OF THIS.

422
00:19:33,473 --> 00:19:36,610
[TOYA] SO TELL ME, DO YOU
