BE LIKE SHIROE?

427
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:48,955
[MINORI] UH...

428
00:19:50,390 --> 00:19:52,025
(MARIELLE SIGHS)

429
00:19:52,125 --> 00:19:54,127
[MARIELLE]
THAT'S IT. I'M DONE.

430
00:19:54,227 --> 00:19:57,097
