HEALTH IS GONE.

431
00:19:57,197 --> 00:19:59,700
[HENRIETTA]
MY BODY WON'T MOVE!
(DOOR OPENS)

432
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:01,668
[MARIELLE] HUH?
[HENRIETTA] THAT SMELL.

433
00:20:01,768 --> 00:20:03,103
