LADIES, SWEETS
DO THE TRICK.

437
00:20:08,108 --> 00:20:10,110
[NYAN‐TA]
MM, YEAH.

438
00:20:10,210 --> 00:20:15,516
YOU GUYS ARE THE BEST,
AND AFTER ALL YOU WENT
THROUGH, TOO, OH, THANK YOU.

439
00:20:15,616 --> 00:20:17,483
[NAOTSUGU] SHIROE KIND OF
ASKED US TO, SO...

440
00:20:17,584 --> 00:20:21,021
[NYAN‐TA] HE SAID YOU'D
PROBABLY BE TIRED WHEN
YOU GOT BACK, AND‐

441
00:20:21,121 --> 00:20:22,222
